    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mortar whose watery consistency allows it to be placed or pumped into small joints or cavities, as between pieces of ceramic clay, slate, or floor tile.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
